item.title: IIMBAA Mobility SIG organises Global Mobility Summit 2024 to drive the revolutionising mobility scenario
item.description: Overall, the Global Mobility Summit 2024 emphasised in advancing IIMBAA Mobility SIG’s mission to make India a key hub for innovation in the global mobility ecosystem. The event not only facilitated rich dialogues but also laid the groundwork for future collaborations that will drive the mobility industry forward.

item.title: 4 Indians Charred In Chilling Multi-Car Crash In US, They Were Carpooling
item.description: Four Indians, including a woman, have died in a massive crash involving five vehicles in US' Texas. The victims had connected through a carpooling app and were on their way to Bentonville in Arkansas on Friday when the tragedy struck.
